        {
            "id": 6308858,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 中台(6923)急拉3.32%報108.5元，成交847張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6923:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6923\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6923-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.32%，13日11:22報108.5元，成交847張，今日漲幅為4.33％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6923:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6923\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6923-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.97%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+489 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+467 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+22 張</li> <li>融資增減：-3 張</li> <li>融券增減：-2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
